HEADWORD: Fortread
<hw>For*tread"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To tread down;
to trample upon.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In hell shall they be all <qex>fortroden</qex> of devils.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

